Please improve JIRA to email all users in the *JIRA Administrators* [Global Permission|http://confluence.atlassian.com/display/JIRA/Managing+Global+Permissions] when a user account becomes locked out, and also make it a configurable setting in the [User Directory|http://confluence.atlassian.com/display/JIRA/Configuring+User+Directories] so admins could opt-out of receiving the email.

